=============================================
Setting up OpenWrt for SatNOGS ground station
=============================================

1. Download the latest OpenWrt stable factory image for TP-Link TL-WR703N (Barrier Breaker 14.07)
2. Flash the image to TLWR703N using the web interface (192.168.1.1 / admin:admin)
3. Set up the router (network, password, wireless, etc) via the web
   interface (http://root@192.168.1.1)
4. Install 'hamlib-easycomm' and 'rtl-sdr' packages
5. scp over 'scripts/satnogs.sh' script to the router (preferably /root)
6. Make satnogs.sh executable (chmod +x satnogs.sh)
7. Add 'satnogs.sh' script to '/etc/rc.local'
8. Reboot router

* OpenWrt wiki - http://wiki.openwrt.org/


